Chapter 1. Admin Guide

   Table of Contents

   1. Overview
   2. BINRPC
   3. Parameters

        3.1. binrpc (string)
        3.2. mode (integer)
        3.3. user (integer or string)
        3.4. group (integer or string)
        3.5. fifo (integer)
        3.6. autoconversion (integer)
        3.7. binrpc_max_body_size (integer)
        3.8. binrpc_struct_max_body_size (integer)

   4. SIP-router RPC Functions

        4.1. ctl.listen
        4.2. ctl.connections
